315868024.Title: Samsung 18 cu. ft. Smart Counter Depth 3-Door French Door Refrigerator, Silver
315868024.Description: 33 in. wide Smart Counter Depth 3-Door French Door Refrigerator is seamlessly designed for a modern, built-in look. Stay connected anywhere, anytime using the SmartThings App. The fingerprint resistant finish withstands everyday smudges, so you spend less time cleaning. Color: Stainless Steel.

303345832.Title: 18.6 cu. ft. French Door Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Counter Depth, Silver
303345832.Description: GE appliances provide up-to-date technology and exceptional quality to simplify the way you live. With a timeless appearance, this family of appliances is ideal for your family. And, coming from one of the most trusted names in America, you know that this entire selection of appliances is as advanced as it is practical. Color: Stainless Steel.

315868464.Title: Samsung 19.4 cu. ft. 3-Door French Door Refrigerator in White
315868464.Description: This Samsung French door refrigerator stores up to 20 bags of groceries and is built for optimal freshness. The Twin Cooling System utilizes independent cooling systems to maintain higher humidity in the refrigerator to keep produce fresher longer, and dry freezer conditions to prevent freezer burn in frozen foods. Surround Air Flow ensures air circulates throughout for even cooling. Plus, LED lighting, Power Freeze and Power Cool Options, and more. Color: White.

206875964.Title: 24.7 cu. ft. French Door Refrigerator in Slate, Fingerprint Resistant and ENERGY STAR, Fingerprint Resistant Slate
206875964.Description: The GNE25JMKES 24.8 cu. ft. French Door Refrigerator in Slate offers an array of features for your convenience, including a factory-installed ice maker and FrostGuard defrost technology. It also features LED lighting, positioned throughout the interior and under fresh food doors to spotlight foods inside both the refrigerator and freezer. And with GE's exclusive Pure and Clean Filtration system, you have the peace of mind that your water is fresh and clean. Color: Fingerprint Resistant Slate.
